title: Refocusing on Weight Loss Basics in the New Year
itunes:title: Refocusing on Weight Loss Basics in the New Year
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Today we talk about all the things you should NOT do on January 1st!

It's so common to want to overhaul everything about our diet and make all these New Year's resolutions. Changing everything at once never works. It throws us right into overwhelm and burnout.
